sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Orchestrator
    participant Ingester
    participant Extractor
    participant LLM as Ingester LLM
    participant Index as FAISS Index
    participant Emitter
    participant Judge
    participant GhostSim as Ghost Simulator

    User->>Orchestrator: ageom ingest "ppg.py" --class PPGProcessor
    Orchestrator->>Ingester: ingest(source, class_name)

    Note over Ingester,Extractor: Phase 1: Deterministic Extraction

    Ingester->>Extractor: extract_ast_data_flow()
    Extractor->>Extractor: Parse AST, trace `self.*` reads/writes
    Extractor->>Extractor: Detect config-gated branches (if self.options.X)
    Extractor-->>Ingester: RawDataFlowGraph

    Note over Ingester,Index: Phase 2: Agentic Semantic Chunking

    loop LangGraph: Propose & Critique (max 3 retries)
        Ingester->>LLM: Group methods into Macro-Atoms<br/>(SEMANTIC_CHUNK prompt + DFG)
        LLM-->>Ingester: ProposedMacroPlan

        Ingester->>LLM: Hoist persistent state into typed models<br/>(HOIST_STATE prompt)
        LLM-->>Ingester: Pydantic Edge Definitions

        loop For internal operations
            Ingester->>Index: search_by_embedding(operation)
            Index-->>Ingester: Existing catalog primitives
            Ingester->>Ingester: Map to "zoom-in" sub-graph
        end

        Ingester->>Ingester: Critic: verify all `self.*` state is preserved

        alt Validation passes
            Note over Ingester: ValidatedMacroPlan ready
        else Validation fails
            Ingester->>Ingester: Prepare retry context with missing state
        end
    end

    Note over Ingester,GhostSim: Phase 3: Emission & Verification

    loop Repair Loop (max 3 retries)
        Ingester->>Emitter: generate_artifacts(ValidatedMacroPlan)
        Emitter->>Emitter: Emit Pydantic models (History as an Edge)
        Emitter->>Emitter: Emit stateless @register_atom wrappers
        Emitter->>Emitter: Emit Ghost Witnesses
        Emitter->>Emitter: Build macro CDGExport + sub-graphs
        Emitter-->>Ingester: IngestionBundle

        Ingester->>Judge: verify_types(source_code)
        Note over Judge: Uses Python ProofEnv (mypy --strict)
        Judge-->>Ingester: VerificationResult

        alt Compilation successful
            Ingester->>GhostSim: run_ghost_simulation(cdg, witnesses)
            GhostSim-->>Ingester: GhostSimReport

            alt Simulation passed
                Note over Ingester: Break repair loop
            else Structural mismatch
                Ingester->>LLM: Fix edge shapes/types<br/>(FIX_GHOST_ERROR prompt)
                LLM-->>Ingester: Patched code plan
            end
        else Type checking failed
            Ingester->>LLM: Fix type annotations<br/>(FIX_TYPE_ERROR prompt)
            LLM-->>Ingester: Patched code plan
        end
    end

    Ingester-->>Orchestrator: IngestionBundle
    Orchestrator->>Orchestrator: Write extracted library to disk
    Orchestrator->>Index: Trigger index build for new atoms
    Orchestrator-->>User: Extracted Library Atoms + Composable CDG